---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
    <h1>
        About me
    </h1>
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="/profile-pic.png" alt="A profile photo of Emilia Williamson" class="profile-image" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;" />
    </div>
    <div class="bio-container">
        <p>
            I'm Emilia, also known as Milly. I'm a software engineer based in Stoke-on-Trent, UK. 
        </p>
        <p>
            As a young teen, I was learned to make websites using HTML, CSS, PHP and MySQL, and I was absolutely obsessed with it. I remember making websites with table layouts and anime hero banners edited in Corel Paint Shop Pro, and uploading them via FTP. At the time, I didn't know it was something that could be a viable career (let alone a lucrative one), and I ended up going down a different path. But the love of making things on the web never left me, and I'm so happy to be back doing it now.
        </p>
        <p>
            In 2022, I decided to make a career change into software development, after working in advice and guidance roles for over half a decade. I've found that my humanities background (English Degree, Law GDL and customer-facing experience) has been a huge asset in my software engineering career, giving me strong communication skills and a user-centric mindset that I bring to my work every day.
        </p>
        <p>
            As of today, I'm a mid-level full stack developer with experience in a range of technologies including TypeScript, React/Next.js, Node.js, REST APIs, SQL and some DevOps. 
        </p>
    </div>
</Layout>
